summary: An ordinance vacating a portion of Water Street (now Elliott Avenue West), lying westerly of Lots 11, 10, 9, 5 and 6, Block 18, D. T. Denny's Water Front Addition, as the same is recorded in Volume 2 of Plats, Page 61, Records of King County, and that portion of the alley in said Block 18, lying southwesterly of the southwesterly line of Western Avenue, as the same was extended and established by Ordinance No. 23040.
